      globalExplanation: 'Environment variables are the highest-priority override in Claude Code. ANTHROPIC_MODEL overrides the model, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY sets the API key, and ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL redirects to a different endpoint (Bedrock, Vertex, or a proxy).',
